title: Science Practice Test 2
intro_text:
Science

Welcome to the Science Practice Test.

You have 40 minutes to complete the test. There are 25 questions. The goal is to give you practice on the types of questions you will see on the GED® test and to help us understand what you need to brush up on for the test.

If you are unsure of an answer click “Review Question Later” to come back to the question later. Try to answer every question.

Relax and do your best!
